Paper 2026: Supercell storm run package

This folder contains everything needed to run the ordinary storm case (aside from the CM1 build):

  - namelist.input
  - carp_force

How to run
1) Create a CM1 run directory.
2) Copy these two files into the run directory:
     namelist.input -> ./namelist.input
     carp_force     -> ./carp_force
3) Build CM1 from this repository and run CM1 in the run directory.

Notes
- NewIF parameters (N0, beta, etc.) are edited in the source via:
    !<IFINP_USER_SETTINGS>
  then CM1 is rebuilt and rerun.
